rows.label: qst701701_msg0001
rows.name:
Strewth, you lot get around, don't ya?
Seems not a day goes by I don't hear
your names. Care to lend me a hand?

rows.label: qst701701_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm huntin' down the no-good drongo
who killed my poor sister. Tracked him
as far as Iira, then lost the trail.

rows.label: qst701701_msg0003
rows.name:
Folks call him the "Silent Specter". He
heads up a pleasant bunch known as
the Bloody Lobsters. That's all I got.

rows.label: qst701701_msg0004
rows.name:
Feels like I've searched every corner of
this Divine Beast for a year or more, and still
no clues. Maybe you can help me out?

rows.label: qst701701_msg0005
rows.name:
Easiest way to help is probably to
gather info. Stick to people who just
arrived in Iira, see what they know.

rows.label: qst701701_msg0006
rows.name:
But listen up. If you find something out,
don't go chasin' him, OK? Come let me
know. He's mine. Got that?

rows.label: qst701701_msg0007
rows.name:
I want to deal with him with my own
hands.
